/F2 15 Tf
1 0 0 1 48.00 465.95 Tm
(E. Data Flow Summary) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 48.00 441.70 Tm
(Authentication/session flow:) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 48.00 425.20 Tm
(- The browser submits credentials to `POST /api/signup` or `POST /api/login`.) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 48.00 411.70 Tm
(- The server validates inputs, hashes or verifies the password, creates a random session token, and returns it.) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 48.00 398.20 Tm
(- The browser stores the token in localStorage and sends it in the `Authorization: Bearer` header.) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 48.00 384.70 Tm
(- The server resolves the token through local JSON or Supabase sessions.) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 48.00 371.20 Tm
(Profile update flow:) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 48.00 354.70 Tm
(- The profile editor collects display name, handle, bio, location, social links, theme, cursor, sparkle, media, and toggle settings.) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 48.00 341.20 Tm
(- The browser sends the profile payload to `PUT /api/profiles/:handle`.) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 48.00 327.70 Tm
(- The server verifies the session and profile ownership before saving.) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 48.00 314.20 Tm
(- Public profile links are saved back onto the user record when possible.) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 48.00 300.70 Tm
(Media upload flow:) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 48.00 284.20 Tm
(- The frontend previews selected files as data URLs.) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 48.00 270.70 Tm
(- In Supabase mode, the server uploads media to `profile-media` and stores object paths.) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 48.00 257.20 Tm
(- In local JSON mode, media remains embedded in profile JSON.) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 48.00 243.70 Tm
(- Public profile media is served through `/api/profiles/:handle/avatar`, `/background`, and `/music`.) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 48.00 230.20 Tm
(Friends/notifications flow:) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 48.00 213.70 Tm
(- Friend requests are stored on the target profile and sent request state is stored on the sender profile.) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 48.00 200.20 Tm
(- Notifications are rendered from friend requests, tribe invites, and tribe join requests.) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 48.00 186.70 Tm
(- The frontend refreshes friend and notification state periodically.) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 48.00 173.20 Tm
(Tribes flow:) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 48.00 156.70 Tm
(- Tribes are owned by the creator and stored inside the owner's profile JSON.) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 48.00 143.20 Tm
(- Tribe summaries are built by scanning all profiles and normalizing their tribe arrays.) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 48.00 129.70 Tm
(- Owner-only actions are enforced by comparing the authenticated user ID with `tribe.ownerId`.) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 48.00 116.20 Tm
(Tribe chat flow:) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 48.00 99.70 Tm
(- Tribe messages are scoped by `tribeId`.) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 48.00 86.20 Tm
(- Messages are stored inside the tribe object and capped at the latest 300 messages.) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
