/F2 15 Tf
1 0 0 1 48.00 459.00 Tm
(1. Executive Summary) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 48.00 434.75 Tm
(fun.lol is a customizable public profile platform where users can create a public bio page, add visual and audio media, connect with) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 48.00 421.25 Tm
(friends, join tribes, chat with tribe members, and play mini-games from a private dashboard. The current product blends a personal) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 48.00 407.75 Tm
(identity page with lightweight social and entertainment features.) Tj
/F2 15 Tf
1 0 0 1 48.00 383.25 Tm
(2. Product Vision) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 48.00 359.00 Tm
(The long-term vision is for fun.lol to become a highly personalized social identity hub. Users should be able to express themselves) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 48.00 345.50 Tm
(through media-rich profiles, share one public link, keep up with friends, create small communities, and enjoy interactive experiences) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 48.00 332.00 Tm
(without leaving the platform.) Tj
/F2 15 Tf
1 0 0 1 48.00 307.50 Tm
(3. Target Users) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 48.00 283.25 Tm
(- Creators who want a personalized profile link.) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 48.00 269.75 Tm
(- Gamers who enjoy expressive profiles and mini-games.) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 48.00 256.25 Tm
(- Social users who want a lightweight friend graph.) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 48.00 242.75 Tm
(- Friend groups who want private-ish spaces around shared identity.) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 48.00 229.25 Tm
(- Community or tribe members who want a shared group and chat.) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 48.00 215.75 Tm
(- Public visitors who open a user's profile link.) Tj
/F2 15 Tf
1 0 0 1 48.00 194.25 Tm
(4. Problem Statement) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 48.00 170.00 Tm
(Many profile-link tools are static, generic, and disconnected from the user's actual social experience. fun.lol solves this by) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 48.00 156.50 Tm
(combining profile customization, media, friend requests, tribe communities, tribe chats, and mini-games in one lightweight web) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 48.00 143.00 Tm
(platform.) Tj
/F2 15 Tf
1 0 0 1 48.00 118.50 Tm
(5. Product Goals) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 48.00 94.25 Tm
(- Enable personal profile customization.) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 48.00 80.75 Tm
(- Support public profile sharing by handle.) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 48.00 67.25 Tm
(- Make social discovery and friend connection simple.) Tj
ET
endstream
